    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Being a shinobi from the Hidden Mist, your village has a long tradition of powerful swordsman. Taking this occupation means that you were trained as a swordsman either by a mentor or even by one of the seven legendary swordsmen from Mist.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Kirigakure Swordsman.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 10+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 3 from Balance, Climb, Chakra Control, Craft (Mechanical), Escape Artist, Gather Information, Hide, Intimidate, Knowledge (ninja lore), Listen, Ninjutsu, Swim, Sleight of Hand, Survival, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Archaic Weapon Proficiency, Armor Proficiency, [Universal: Defensive Stance], Genin, Genjutsu Adept, Monkey Grip, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, [Universal: Risky Strike], Taijutsu Adept.</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +2</p>"
